column2:
"...It seems they've finally defeated Dark Falz...
How's the project coming along?"

"Third Project Progress: 98%.
Photon Induction: 99% of projected levels."

"Tomorrow will mark five hundred years...
It won't be long now until the Day of Arrival."

"Correction: The Day of Arrival will be in
31,415,926 seconds. Margin of error: Plus or minus 0.05--"

"Plan continuation accepted.
Transferring to the next phase."
